Key Match Events: Paolo Banchero scored 34 points and grabbed 7 rebounds in 27 minutes.
Post-Match Reflections: Magic coach Jamahl Mosley praised Banchero's performance and poise.
Banchero expressed frustration over missing time but remained positive.
Banchero mentioned a chip on his shoulder and wanting to make up for lost time.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Orlando Magic are in the No. 4 spot in the Eastern Conference.
Milwaukee Bucks leapfrogged the Magic for the No. 4 spot with their win.
The Magic went 19-11 during Banchero's absence despite dealing with other injuries.
